---
import Breadcrumbs from '@/components/breadcrumbs.astro'
import Link from '@/components/link.astro'
import PageHead from '@/components/page-head.astro'
import Layout from '@/layouts/layout.astro'
---

<Layout class="max-w-3xl">
  <PageHead slot="head" title="About" />
  <Breadcrumbs items={[{ label: 'About', icon: 'lucide:info' }]} />

  <section>
    <div class="min-w-full">
      <div class="prose mb-8">
        <p class="mt-0">
          I am a <strong>Head of AI</strong> and <strong>AI Product Manager</strong> with
          more than a decade of experience connecting advanced analytics with
          high-impact business decisions. My work sits at the intersection of
          strategy, product thinking, and execution: helping teams move from
          isolated experimentation to scalable AI capability.
        </p>
        <p>
          Across banking, energy, and retail, I have led multidisciplinary
          teams delivering AI initiatives, analytical roadmaps, and digital
          transformation programs. I enjoy translating between technical depth
          and executive priorities so that models, platforms, and processes all
          contribute to measurable outcomes.
        </p>
        <h2>What I focus on</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Designing AI and machine learning roadmaps tied to ROI and operational adoption.</li>
          <li>Leading Data and AI products with a balance of technical quality, governance, and business impact.</li>
          <li>Helping organizations build the processes, culture, and delivery discipline needed for sustainable AI.</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Education and toolkit</h2>
        <p>
          My background includes an MSc in Industrial Engineering and a B.Eng.
          in Systems Engineering from Pontificia Universidad Javeriana, plus
          specialization in AI Product Management and MLOps.
        </p>
        <p>
          I regularly work with Python, SQL, PySpark, cloud platforms, and the
          operating practices that make analytics teams effective beyond the
          prototype stage.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <Link href="/projects" underline>
          Browse projects
        </Link>
        <Link href="/blog" underline>
          Read posts
        </Link>
        <Link href="/docs/CV_Daniel_Silva.pdf" underline external>
          Download resume
        </Link>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
